Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:10.80,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:19.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:31.59,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:38.76,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The fifth round of the Royal Knights \NSelection Exam finally concluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.89,main,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Crystal magic stoppage confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:43.18,main,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,B Team wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:44.60,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Fully bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:48.18,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Full bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.18,0:00:49.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,C Team wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:53.69,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Magic: Spiral Flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.46,0:00:57.49,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Crystal destroyed! E Team wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:07.21,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The crystal's been destroyed. G Team wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:11.71,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,Picture Magic: Twin Storms of Fire and Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.29,0:01:17.22,main,Roland,0000,0000,0000,,Sandstone Magic: Rock Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:23.85,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The crystal has been destroyed.\N I Team wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.01,0:01:28.41,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,You guys were pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.41,0:01:31.46,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't quite managed \Nthe ultimate painting yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.22,0:01:36.11,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The sixth round was about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:38.11,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally our turn! I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:41.20,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you don't go \Nrunning off on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:44.70,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hit 'em with our best performances!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:45.83,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:48.64,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And now, for the sixth round of stage one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.64,0:01:49.75,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And... begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:26.01,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Bad Blood
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:30.45,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Things are getting pretty intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:33.42,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Both teams are concentrating \Ntheir attacks at the center
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:35.23,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,of the battlefield for a magic slugfest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:41.49,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Steel Creation Magic: Full Metal Fortress!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:44.98,main,Francis,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:53.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,His spell changed shape! That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:58.00,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,He added a page to his grimoire \Nand evolved the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:04:01.26,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Magic: Thunderbolt Destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:05.84,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,How is his spell so destructive?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:09.47,main,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought... This isn't a junior-level fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:13.36,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Luck and I have done tons of \Nmissions over the last few months,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.36,0:04:15.18,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,and we've gotten tougher every time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:18.90,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't no way we're still junior-level!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:22.06,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,He's always had intermediate skills,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:24.65,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,but apparently, he's gotten stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:27.84,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,But that goes for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:32.25,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Following Asta's example, I trained \Nmy magic, my body, and my spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:37.25,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Even if my hard work may betray me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.85,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I will not betray my hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:43.22,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Steel Creation Magic: Blazing Spiral Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:48.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, four-eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:50.99,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Fantastic, Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:54.48,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're not just some four-eyes \Nwho's too serious and worries too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:59.17,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Nice! After this fight is over,\N you should fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:02.53,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! Concentrate on this match!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:13.00,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes... Rob Vitesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:15.79,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,He's left the crystal behind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:20.42,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We'll bust through our three opponents \Nand destroy the crystal in a single rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:21.80,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:26.06,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,You know... You two are pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:29.51,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,Wing Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:31.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,She's actually flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:34.39,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Flapping!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:36.64,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,That's an attack for the enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:38.81,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:42.60,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,And a tailwind for my allies!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:44.90,italics,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,This is so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:47.07,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Break through!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:50.92,main,Rob,0000,0000,0000,,In the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:53.83,main,Rob,0000,0000,0000,,it's individual power differences\Nthat separate victory and defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:59.13,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,My spell didn't even faze him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:02.50,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,Not good... Crazy boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:03.46,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,More...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:04.96,italics,Rob,0000,0000,0000,,He's fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:09.80,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:16.56,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,In a single blow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:19.74,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The crystal has been destroyed. K Team wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:21.09,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:22.69,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,They did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:24.59,sign_9194_75_Yay____Yay____,Gordon/caps,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Yay, yay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:30.19,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that was so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:32.55,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Luck! Y-You actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:37.05,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,Boom, boom! You two are fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:38.71,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:41.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:45.25,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard! You're getting \Nway too damn strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:51.59,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Our next opponent...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:53.42,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,...seems even more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.42,0:06:55.43,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,...seems like they'll help me make \Nan even better picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:58.97,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Next up, the eighth and \Nfinal round of stage one...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:01.35,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,O Team and P Team, step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:04.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Which means it's finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:04.86,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:08.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,...time for Yuno and Noelle's team!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:10.34,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, it's our turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:13.27,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,After we're done here, \Nyou're going on a date with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.27,0:07:14.62,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:16.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The other guy....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:19.77,top,En,0000,0000,0000,,Let's... do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:23.15,sign_10482_94_Green_Praying_Ma,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(485,750)}The Green Praying Mantises 4th Class Senior Magic Knight\N{\fs30}En Ringard
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:22.13,top,En,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will be okay \Nif we work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:24.38,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Are {\i1}you{\i0} okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:26.87,main,En,0000,0000,0000,,Let's win... no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:30.18,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is he going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:31.38,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:35.21,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,And I heard that you grew up with Stupidsta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:37.97,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you're not as reckless as he is, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:42.10,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking. You can't \Ncontrol your magic well, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:44.77,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like it took all \Nyou had to maintain
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:46.36,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,your Mana Skin at the volcano.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:48.57,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Can you actually fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:52.17,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! I'm royalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:58.58,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Can you actually think and fight, you violent\N peasant who's Asta's childhood friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:00.31,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,What a noisy woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:02.64,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't even an argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:06.29,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,That lame comeback... \NIs Asta rubbing off on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:09.99,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Why would I ever \Nbe influenced by him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.99,0:08:13.30,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,See?! You're just like Shtupidshta!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:16.46,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. Guess I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:18.93,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm perfectly calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:22.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you two, grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:24.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Learn to get along already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:26.94,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I think you might be the \Ncause of this, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:30.19,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about you, Asta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:33.70,main,En,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly... Why don't \Nwe come up with a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:37.62,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Who said you could touch me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:41.54,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're having a friendly chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:46.54,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,It's as though you think you \Nactually have the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:49.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Bulls just happened to \Nmake a good showing for once,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:52.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and you really believe it was thanks to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Solid...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:58.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't control your magic,\Nand despite being from the House of Silva,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:01.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,you couldn't even make it \Ninto the Silver Eagles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:03.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're going to fight {\i1}me{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:07.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're back again, shaggy bangs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:12.78,flashback,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,You failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:18.03,flashback,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you do the same things \Nas us when you're also royalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:23.56,flashback,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Trash! How dare you eat before me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:31.55,flashback,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop, Solid. Please give that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.93,0:09:36.51,flashback,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,You can't protect what's important \Nto you because you're weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:38.51,flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:48.23,flashback,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,If you're upset, then get back at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:52.52,flashbackitalics,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,If you can actually hit me \Nwith your spells, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:09:59.99,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, you thieving raccoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:03.95,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,The fairy dust! The fairy dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:08.10,sign_9194_75_Yay____Yay____,Gordon/caps,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Don't worry. You can do it. \NWe all worked so hard together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:09.85,sign_9194_75_Yay____Yay____,Gordon/caps,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}We're basically family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:14.48,sign_9194_75_Yay____Yay____,Gordon/caps,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}We know you way better than \Nthat brother of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:19.24,sign_9194_75_Yay____Yay____,Gordon/caps,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Now, believe in your friends \Nand yourself! Believe yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:21.93,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What's he mumbling about over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:25.97,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's cursing that \Nannoying brother of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:28.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:29.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're up. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:30.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:34.98,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you do your \Nbest to run away, Noelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:37.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyah, nyah, nyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:40.24,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's finally end this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:56.25,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We will now begin the \Neighth round of stage one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:11:02.29,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,O Team: Sandler, Dimitri, and Solid \Nversus P Team: En, Noelle, and Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:11:03.51,sign_15736_152_Sandler,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(459,1)\blur3}Sandler
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:11:03.51,sign_10657_103_Nix,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(459,1)\blur3}Dimitri
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:11:03.51,sign_15736_154_Solid,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(459,1)\blur3}Solid
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:11:03.51,sign_15736_155_O_Team,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(459,1)\blur3}O Team
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:11:03.51,sign_15736_156_En___Noelle___Yu,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(459,1)\blur3}En   Noelle   Yuno
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:11:03.51,sign_15736_157_P_Team,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(459,1)\blur3}P Team
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:03.51,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:06.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You've got this, Yuno and Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:12.76,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle! Show them what the \NBlack Bulls' women are made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:17.53,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle! No need to hold back \Njust because he's your brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:20.61,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll attack. You two support me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:22.22,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'll attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:23.03,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,No, me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:24.07,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,No, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:24.92,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:26.21,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.21,0:11:28.70,main,En,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll support...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.26,0:11:32.11,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,This fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:33.42,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:41.17,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,This is an annoying way to do it, but it's \Na shortcut with a simplified version
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:43.42,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,of that compound magic from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:47.22,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,We'll end this instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:50.74,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't moved their crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:53.94,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good. They closed the \Ndistance to our crystal in one sprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.51,0:11:58.28,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Wind Magic: Crescent Moon Sickle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:02.11,main,Dimitri,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Magic: Combo Eruption!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:05.53,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Water Magic: Sea Dragon's Lair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.03,0:12:11.66,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Look at you, learning a defense spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:15.17,main,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,Sand Magic: Suppressing Sand Mass!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:21.42,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's sucking up the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.43,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we'll spend the \Nwhole match on the defensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:32.27,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who gave you permission \Nto cling to him like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:36.06,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm probably the fastest on this team.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:39.65,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take advantage of that \Nand go destroy their crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:43.93,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,While I'm doing that, you two \Nsomehow protect our crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:45.20,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:46.94,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:48.87,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:54.58,main,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,None of you will be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:01.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You go, Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:04.41,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,She's been fighting alongside Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.46,0:13:06.89,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:12.85,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's safer if I'm the one \Nprotecting the crystal, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:14.85,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,If I go...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:17.38,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there, Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:20.15,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Solid's bound to come after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:23.07,main,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go off on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:30.08,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:34.92,flashbackitalics,Guy 1,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear about the \Nnewbie with the four-leaf clover?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:39.08,flashback,Guy 1,0000,0000,0000,,He actually defeated one of the\N Eight Shining Generals from Diamond!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:42.84,flashback,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? That's insane for his first year!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:46.07,flashback,Guy 1,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but when he did it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:49.56,flashback,Guy 1,0000,0000,0000,,he told the vice captain that he was going \Nto become the Captain of the Golden Dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:51.71,flashback,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.71,0:13:54.97,flashback,Guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you have to be on a different \Nlevel when the Wind Spirit chooses you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:58.69,flashbackitalics,Guy 1,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Captain Vangeance \Nhas high hopes for him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:04.11,main,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying you're going to guard \Nthe crystal while dealing with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:07.99,main,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,That attitude is sheer insolence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.99,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Please come at me with everything you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:15.40,italics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,Why you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:19.52,sign_14555_151_4_years_ago,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(502,996)}Several Years Ago
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:25.26,flashbackitalics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't expecting an ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:29.67,flashbackitalics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,As I was running, I fell deep into this cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:32.89,flashbackitalics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,No one will be able to rescue me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:35.95,flashbackitalics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:43.52,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Alecdora?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:45.80,italics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,He looked just like
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:48.94,italics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,the figure in a painting \NI saw when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:51.21,italics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,The figure of a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:57.95,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,I sensed you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:00.18,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:08.22,italics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,Master Vangeance has some other \Nmysterious power besides magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:14.18,italics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,A warm power that seems to connect \Nhim to his squad members.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:19.53,italics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,I swore that I'd devote my \Ngrimoire to his service.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:25.17,italics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,I worked hard to ensure that the \NGolden Dawn remained the strongest squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:32.47,italics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,We are an elite team of nobles \Nchosen by Master Vangeance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:36.79,italics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,So why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:39.42,italics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that peasant in our midst?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:42.54,italics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.78,italics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:48.80,italics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,Master Vangeance always interacted with \Nall his squad members equally, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:52.30,italics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,With that boy... With him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:53.74,flashback,William,0000,0000,0000,,Yuno...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:58.47,flashback,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,He's called him by name five times today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:01.81,flashback,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he hasn't even \Nspoken to me once yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:05.31,italics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,Why him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:07.82,italics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because of his four-leaf clover?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.81,italics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,And that boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.81,0:16:12.73,italics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,The one Master Vangeance \Nexpects great things from
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.73,0:16:15.32,italics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,said that he would become captain himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:18.08,italics,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,He's mocking Master Vangeance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:22.58,main,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get full of yourself just because \Nyou lucked into getting spirit magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:25.96,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Getting chosen by me was \Npart of Yuno's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:29.00,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's pissing me off!\N Let's get him, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:30.81,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Step back, Bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:34.59,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning on fighting \Nwithout my powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:45.49,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just keep defending, Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:47.15,main,Dimitri,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:51.61,main,Dimitri,0000,0000,0000,,You're ruining our strategy! Both of us\N are supposed to hit the crystal together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:54.78,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Don't boss me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:58.28,main,Dimitri,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'll join you,\Nand we'll defeat her in one—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:16:59.95,main,Mush,0000,0000,0000,,Heya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:03.45,main,Dimitri,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:12.23,main,En,0000,0000,0000,,Fungus Magic: Running Mister Mushroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.23,0:17:15.21,main,En,0000,0000,0000,,I put some spores on you a little earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:17.93,main,En,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get in Noelle's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:23.68,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, Noelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:25.53,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've caught up with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:29.44,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,you don't have a chance in hell \Nof scratching our crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:33.16,main,Mush,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be too sure about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:36.34,main,Mush,0000,0000,0000,,Relax. I's me, En.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:39.45,main,Mush,0000,0000,0000,,This is Talking Mushroom. \NIt lets you hear my voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:43.04,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave you permission to \Nstick this thing on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:45.66,main,Mush,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:49.92,italics,En,0000,0000,0000,,I heard Solid's remarks before the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.92,0:17:53.05,italics,En,0000,0000,0000,,A big brother should never say \Nsuch things to his little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:57.25,italics,En,0000,0000,0000,,I have ten younger brothers and sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:17:59.98,italics,En,0000,0000,0000,,They're the ones I'm fighting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:06.56,main,En,0000,0000,0000,,Big brothers exist to protect the younger, \Nweaker siblings born after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:10.44,main,En,0000,0000,0000,,And yet you've only said \Nhurtful things to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:13.82,main,En,0000,0000,0000,,Get him, Noelle! Thrash your brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:19.14,main,En,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just give him an ordinary thrashing! \NMake sure he never defies you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:22.35,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right... You sure are energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:27.62,main,En,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are animals, too! Once you put \Nthem in their place, they won't turn on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:33.56,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Who's going to thrash whom, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.56,0:18:39.62,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way a failure \Nlike you could beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:44.18,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I was weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:49.95,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You've always been strong, so you probably \Ncan't understand how weak people feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:55.08,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,At this point, I don't care if \Nyou ever acknowledge me or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:19:00.74,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Because even greater people\N have acknowledged me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:05.06,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I used to be really scared \Nof your magic, Solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:07.91,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But now, it feels really flimsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:11.71,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep running your mouth, \Nyou embarrassment to the House of Silva!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:15.03,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Slashing Sea Serpent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:19.13,main,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,How much more do you intend to insult me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:23.89,main,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,Sand Creation Magic: \NSand-Armored Heavy Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:28.49,main,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,This spell contains all the attack \Nand defense powers that I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.49,0:19:31.90,main,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can stop it \Nwithout your spirit magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:36.40,main,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who will make \NMaster Vangeance's dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:40.95,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Wind Magic: Towering Tornado!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:47.41,main,Sandler,0000,0000,0000,,From the inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:52.56,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? He activated his \Nspell inside his opponent's spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:57.80,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,He can even do that? That's what \Nseparates us from hot guys, dang it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.23,0:20:07.18,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about \Nother people's dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:13.48,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,The only dreams I see are my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:18.12,italics,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:19.54,italics,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:21.69,italics,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be real!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.50,italics,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,What's that spell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:30.41,italics,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious! \NNoelle couldn't cast a spell like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:32.41,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Solid...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:38.04,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right if I hit you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:40.76,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Just go ahead and try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:45.84,italics,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,It won't hit me! There's no way \Nher spell could actually hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:49.10,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,You complete failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:51.85,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Dragon's Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:03.54,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:05.61,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,She destroyed the crystal in a single blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:09.30,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The crystal has been destroyed! P Team wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:16.93,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not weak anymore!
